reviewText: Want to work on thighs and back of arms as well as general conditioing.  Here it is.
GREAT VIDEO...VERY VERSATILE WITH COMBINED AEROBIC AND ANAEROBIC MOVES

I have had this video for over 10 years and I absolutely LOVE it!  I highly recommend it for anyone who is starting out after being sedentary for quite awhile or who simply wants to incorporate some exercise into their day without being too "gung-ho."  Victoria is THE BEST.

This video will work you.  Victoria reminds you to protect yourself while you workout.  I own several of her vidoes and everytime I get motivated to lose weight, she always help me do it and keep me motivated.  This girl can move.  Its worth the 30 minutes a day.
